headline: CWAN Honors Investment Management Leaders with 2025 Excellence Awards
summary: BOISE, Idaho, September 17, 2025--Clearwater Analytics (NYSE: CWAN), the most comprehensive technology platform for investment management, today announced the winners of its Client Excellence Awards at its annual user conference Connect ‘25. The awards spotlight the industry pioneers who are setting new standards in investment management operations through transformational technology and operational breakthroughs.
